content: I’ve done the training can I just go to website & make calls tomorrow? Btw awesome calling website

Hey Owen! You'll want to go to the Call Guide to get the right dialer link and info about where we are calling. And then you can hang out in <#1242256751445934262> to connect with other callers and let us know how it is going! Thanks for diving in!

https://txt.democrats.org/Call-Guide

Monday’s calls are 2p-10p ET / 11a-7p PT

Also right now the dialer link is only in Slack. We're working on getting it over here, but you can join Slack here - https://txt.democrats.org/SlackJoin
